{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act33side", "eventName": "巴別塔", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BB-9", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "塵埃落定", "storyInfo": "重傷的特蕾西婭憑著最後的力氣將“文明的存續”交給了阿米婭，而在此時出現在特蕾西婭面前的人是博士。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_light", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭最後記得的事，是她睡在黑色的泡泡裡。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭溫柔地抱著包裹著她的泡泡。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "講述著一個她已經聽過許多次的故事……"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在絕望的沙漠裡有很多恐怖的影子，他們追逐著不停尋找希望的小布人。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑袍的影子是最古老最古老的，絕望和悲哀的回聲。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旦被他們抓住，就再也逃不開了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在沙漠中，小布人遇到了綴滿赤金與寶石的國王，他答應小布人只要原路返回，就給他數不盡的財富。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管國王拉扯著他，小布人依舊丟下了誘人的寶石繼續前進。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但很快——", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑袍的影子追上了他。影子不斷向他撲去，無窮無盡……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“砰，砰，砰”……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只能抽出針和線做的長矛與黑色的影子戰鬥，最終擋開了影子們的利爪繼續向前逃去……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到逃到一條淚水匯成的大河。沒有船隻，沒有浮萍，小布人只能游過去……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可一沾上淚水，他就越來越沉，直至河底——", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#3$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他失敗了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#6$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是故事的結局了嗎？阿米婭不願意相信。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是特蕾西婭小姐念錯了也說不定？"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她焦急地想要讓特蕾西婭小姐改變結局……"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#6$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭小姐……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我在。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們……能救救小布人嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要救他嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想，我……很想很想……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_underwtr", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "un"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "un", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聲音淡去了。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擋住阿米婭視線的泡泡在消散。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭的身影在她的眼前越來越清晰——"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g10_theresaoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "un", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.4, "b": 0.3, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在眼角的餘光中，她看到了躺倒在地面上的黑袍影子們滲出的殷紅。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些人……是誰？他們是什麼時候來的？為什麼會躺在地上？"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭有太多太多的疑惑想要問特蕾西婭，她努力睜大自己的眼睛……"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看到了白色衣服上沾染的殷紅。看到了……特蕾西婭泛紅的眼角。"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭小姐還好嗎？"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭想問問特蕾西婭小姐身上的傷勢。"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她發不出聲音。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……阿米婭，沒事。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這呢。那些故事裡的壞蛋已經暫時被打倒了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭小姐怎麼了？"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭想要拭去特蕾西婭小姐臉上的疲憊。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她抬不起自己的手。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i17", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.15, "yScaleTo": 1.15, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我沒有能力改變故事的結局。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是你可以，阿米婭……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會走上一條艱難的道路。就像試圖跨越淚水之河的小布人。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能夠幫上你的，唯有將這頂黑色的冠冕贈與你。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬年的時間，我的族群因為歷史的局限性，錯誤地使用了這頂冠冕。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它被污染，被綁定。但本不該如此。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果要打破詛咒，打破命運……我需要你的幫助。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你願意改寫結局嗎？", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭想要說出“願意”，但她無法發出聲音。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她焦急地點著頭，她想，也許至少這樣能夠幫上特蕾西婭小姐……"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能夠救她——"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我現在剩下的力量能做的不多，但足以將它的權限轉移給你。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為你封存了它的大部分區域，以免無邊無際的訊息攪亂你的思緒。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭……抱歉，我將這頂冠冕的重量壓在了你的身上。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本以為……我能夠陪伴你的日子還有好久好久，陪伴你長大，陪伴你到能勇敢地面對父母的離去，陪伴你到能自己給出回答——", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回答你是否願意替我繼續走下去……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但留給我們的時間總是不夠，阿米婭。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我如今自私地將我所背負的重擔壓在了你的身上……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，孩子——", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_daggerslow", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "49_i19", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 15.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭試圖喊出聲，但她卻無法張開口，甚至無法挪動自己的四肢。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑色的劍刃似乎穿透了自己的胸口。"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她理應感受到痛苦。但那柄劍留下的——"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有溫熱。充滿期盼的溫熱。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，它是希望，亦是痛苦。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會困惑，會猶疑。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但請相信，凱爾希醫生會永遠站在你的身邊。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她會幫助你去探究，去重新接近存續的秘密。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能克服的，對吧，阿米婭……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直都是一個堅強到令我都驚訝的孩子。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真的很累了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，阿米婭，這些日子，是你將快樂帶給了我。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，先暫且休息片刻吧。睡吧……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安心地睡吧。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會一直陪著你。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g10_theresaoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭聽到了熟悉的聲音。"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……阿米婭！", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭並未抬頭看向到來的人。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王冠抽離，又重聚。而她的氣息卻愈發微弱。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……博士。你何必來到這裡呢。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_048"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_048"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我感到了……你的情感。我看見了，你的過去。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你本可以待在別處，靜待我的死亡到來。你知道這一次，我不會逃離，也不會撤退。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你來，是為了找阿米婭嗎？還是為了……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭已經不用聽那個人的回答。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那人的身後，潮水般的刺客不斷從陰影中湧來，奔向了特蕾西婭——"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你的答案吧，博士……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}